                  "revisionId": 2617494,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Can be combined with Carnis Stinger and Razor Shot to provide a 300% increase to Slash damage."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Maim",
                  "pageId": 548600,
                  "revisionId": 2617494,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "When calculating total raw damage, a weapon will require a Slash damage percentage equal to 75% of its total base damage to equal the raw damage increase provided by a standard elemental mod (which increases corresponding elemental damages by 90%). The higher the Slash damage percentage over 75%, the more viable this mod will be as opposed to an elemental mod, and vice versa for lower values. These calculations only pertain to raw damage, and do not take into consideration enemy armor/flesh/shield damage multipliers."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Maim",
                  "pageId": 548600,
                  "revisionId": 2617494,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Due to this comparison, the only secondaries to effectively use Maim as a damage increase mod are Pyrana , Akjagara Prime and Euphona Prime 's secondary shot, as all other weapons have 70% ratio or less."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Maim",
                  "pageId": 548600,
                  "revisionId": 2617494,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Titania 's Dex Pixia are also able to effectively use this mod, having a ratio of 80% slash."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Maim",
                  "pageId": 548600,
                  "revisionId": 2617494,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "That being said, this mod can still be effectively used to increase the chance of slash procs in status builds, given how the type of damage amounts affects the calculations for procs."
                }
              }
